aS'<p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">Steigerwalt Law Firm is a <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">DUI lawyer in San Diego</a> </p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">Ways to Prevent <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego Drunk Driving<p /></a></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">The clink of glasses marks most celebrations.&#160; Given that people will probably drink at social events and special occasions, it is important to drink responsibly.<p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">This means using good judgment before getting behind the wheel of a car or allowing others to drive in an alcohol-impaired condition.&#160; The findings of a survey conducted by the NHTSA, or National Highway Traffic Safety Administration, revealed that four out of five Americans identified drunk driving as a major threat to their safety and that of their families.<p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">Despite this information, the survey also indicated that eight percent of those age 16 and older admitted they rode in a car even though the driver likely consumed too much alcohol to drive safely.<p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><b mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Select a designated driver<p /></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">To prevent unfortunate and costly accidents due to drunk driving, here are some suggestions for serving alcohol responsibly at social gatherings:<p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Before the party starts, choose someone as the designated driver for the evening and give the car keys to that person <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Stop serving alcohol to anyone who appears intoxicated <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Have non-alcoholic beverages readily available <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Do not make drinks with high amounts of alcohol <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Stop serving alcohol a few hours before the party is scheduled to end <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Eat food high in protein or carbohydrates because they absorb alcohol at a higher rate than sugary foods <p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">If you must drive to social gatherings, advance planning can keep you and others safe.&#160; By never driving in an alcohol-impaired condition, you and your passengers can reach your destinations safely. And that is really something worth celebrating.</p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">For more information about <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI law</a>, please visit our website <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com/">http://www.sdcountydui.com</a>.&#160; Steigerwalt Law Firm is a <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI attorney</a>. <p /></p>'
