onsultation. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur office will start working on your case immediately and begin gathering the\r\nwitness statements and evidence to prove and win your case. Call us now at <b>(800) 606-1717</b> to speak with one our experienced <a href="http://www.buckfirelaw.com/" target="&#95;blank" title="Michigan Personal Injury Lawyers">Michigan personal injury lawyers</a>.</p>'
