aS'<p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">Last December, after receiving 250 adverse event reports related to Pradaxa (Dabigatran), the Food and Drug Administration (FDA) launched an investigation into fatal bleeding associated with <a href="http://www.unsafe-drug-lawyers.com/pradaxa-related-deaths-reported.php">Pradaxa</a>.&#160; Despite Pradaxa now being linked to more than500 deaths, the FDA reported last Friday that Pradaxa does not have a higher risk of bleeding than for patients taking Coumadin (Warafin).&#160; However, that does not mean that Pradaxa is safer than Coumadin. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">Both Pradaxa and Coumadin are anticoagulants, commonly known as blood thinners.&#160; Pradaxa is prescribed to reduce the risk of clotting for patients with atrial fibrillation (A-fib). A-Fib is a condition in which irregular heart beats increase the chance of clots forming in the body and possibly causing a stroke. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText"><p>&#160;</p></p><p TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">While fatal bleeding may be one of the <a href="http://central-pennsylvania.legalexaminer.com/fda-and-prescription-drugs/pradaxa-side-effects-related-deaths.aspx?googleid=298292">side effects of blood thinners</a>, it is more serious for patients taking Dabigatran, because none of the antidotes for serious bleeding work on the drug.&#160;&#160; <a href="http://central-pennsylvania.legalexaminer.com/fda-and-prescription-drugs/pradaxa-side-effects-related-deaths.aspx?googleid=298292">Dabigatran side effects</a> are non-reversible. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">Boehringer Ingelheim, the German manufacturer of Pradaxa is working on an antidote to treat fatal bleeding caused its drug.&#160; Complaints about the FDA&#8217;s approval process have come from the medical community and family members of victims killed by Pradaxa. The insufficient approval process allowed a potentially dangerous drug to be sold without an option for reversing its side effects. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">In the meantime, patients taking Pradaxa should talk with their doctor about the side effects and make sure Pradaxa is right for them.&#160;&#160; </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoBodyText">You should seek medical attention immediately if you experience unexplained bruising, blood in the urine or stool, coughing or vomiting up blood, unexplained bleeding or uncontrollable bleeding.&#160; Early detection of <a href="http://www.unsafe-drug-lawyers.com/pradaxa-related-deaths-reported.php">Dabigatran side effects</a> may increase chances of recovery. </p>\r\n<p><a href="https://plus.google.com/103224636578810205141/posts " target="blank" rel="author">Read more about Michael Monheit on Google+</a></p>'
