aS'\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">Although\r\nmost of us already associate pain with visiting a dentist, orthodontist or oral\r\nsurgeon, we need to realize that we can suffer far more serious problems if we\r\nsee the wrong dental professional. &#160;When\r\nproper procedures aren&#8217;t followed, dental patients can suffer permanent facial paralysis,\r\n<a href="www.injury-attorneys.com" target="&#95;blank">brain damage</a> or even blindness. &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">If\r\nyou&#8217;re not pleased with your current dentist, make sure you carefully survey your\r\nfriends to obtain the names of the ones they like and visit regularly so you\r\ncan choose the best one possible. Once you\'ve done that, personally check to be\r\nsure your new dentist, oral surgeon or orthodontist conducts his or her office\r\nin a highly responsible, patient-friendly manner.&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">The\r\nfollowing list describes some &quot;red flags&quot; or warnings about office\r\npractices that may indicate that it&#8217;s time to find a new dental professional. </p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal"><u>Practices\r\nof Unprofessional Dentists/Orthodontists/Oral Surgeons</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nFailing\r\nto have patients fill out detailed medical history forms, clearly indicating\r\ntheir chronic medical conditions and current prescription drug dosages;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nFailing\r\nto obtain proper consent forms from patients before handling any major dental\r\nprocedures or surgeries. When that isn&#8217;t done, chances are the doctor is also\r\nfailing to clearly explain the risks of all upcoming procedures as well;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDamaging\r\na patient&#8217;s teeth or gums by creating a crown, bridge or &#8220;night guard&#8221; that\r\ndoesn\'t fit properly &#8211; without offering to construct a better one, free of\r\ncharge;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nFailing\r\nto recognize the early signs of temporomandibular joint disorder, also known as\r\n&#8220;TMJ Syndrome;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nUsing\r\nthe wrong type of anesthesia or dosage while performing a surgical procedure on\r\na patient;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nCarelessly\r\nallowing serious infections or injuries to develop in a patient&#8217;s mouth by not\r\ntaking proper safety precautions;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nFailing\r\nto properly diagnose or treat periodontal diseases or forms of oral cancer;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nSpending\r\ninsufficient time explaining all of a patient\'s treatment options prior to scheduling\r\nadditional appointments;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast">??&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nBeing\r\nunwilling or unable to give patients the names of competent orthodontists and\r\noral surgeons in the same area who can handle critical procedures that are\r\nbeyond the professional&#8217;s skill level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal"><u>&#160;</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal"><u>Referrals</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"><u>&#160;</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">Always keep in mind\r\nthat the best dentists and related specialists are usually quite eager to refer\r\npatients to other professionals once they realize that a person&#8217;s needs lie\r\noutside their areas of expertise. Never try to save yourself some money by\r\nletting your regular dentist try to tackle a complicated procedure for which he\r\nor she has not been properly trained. </p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">Don&#8217;t be shy\r\nabout learning more about the experience level of any dental professional\r\nwanting to do work in your mouth. Ask how many times the individual has performed\r\na suggested procedure in the past. &#160;Keep\r\nin mind that a second opinion may not only preserve your best oral health, it\r\ncan actually lead you to a better trained doctor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">While most\r\ndentists, orthodontists and oral surgeons perform their professionals tasks in\r\na highly competent manner, our firm recognizes that you may need to talk to\r\nsomeone regarding a major procedure that appears to have gone seriously wrong.\r\nFeel free to call our office so that one of our attorneys can schedule a free,\r\nno-commitment<a name="&#95;GoBack"></a> appointment for you so we can help you\r\ndecide if you need to take legal action against your healthcare provider.</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;" class="MsoNormal">The <a href="http://www.injury-attorneys.com/">Demas Law Group</a> has been providing the highest quality of legal services to\r\nCalifornians for nearly twenty years. We take great pride in meeting our\r\nclients&#8217; needs while working together to win your case and obtain the maximum\r\ncompensation allowed by law. We are here to help you during this difficult\r\ntime. Call our team of Sacramento personal injury lawyers at 888 776 0977 to\r\nspeak with an attorney. To learn more about why you should hire us <a href="http://www.injury-attorneys.com/top-reasons-to-hire-demas-law-group.html">click here</a>.</p>'
