aS'<br /><p>When you are injured due to the willful or negligent actions of another, a personal injury law firm can help you receive compensation commensurate with your injuries and the circumstances of your case. </p><p>Many types of injuries are caused by the negligence of others. These injuries range from those you can recover from in time, such as fractures, to catastrophic injuries that cause serious, life-altering damage, such as brain and spinal injuries. Personal injury lawyers can help you fight for settlements that cover all the medical care you require and replace the income you can no longer earn. </p><p><b>Common categories of personal injuries caused by negligence</b></p><p><a href="http://personal-injury.lawyers.com/" target="&#95;blank">Personal injury</a> cases are often grouped into categories that include the following:</p><ul><li>Motor vehicle accidents involving cars, trucks, motorcycles, and buses</li><li>Other types of transportation accidents, such as those that occur on boats, trains, and aircraft</li><li>Workplace accidents, such as those that occur on construction sites, in mines, in warehouses, on ships, and in factories</li><li>Medical malpractice, such as misdiagnosed illnesses, surgical errors, and incorrect prescriptions</li><li>Product liability cases, such as the sudden acceleration of cars, toys with lead, or unsafe drugs</li></ul><p>While negligence is a common thread to all bona fide personal injury claims or lawsuits, each type of accident case requires a different legal approach. The legal strategy that works best for medical malpractice may not be effective for suing manufacturers of dangerous or defective products. For this reason, it is important to find a personal injury lawyer with considerable experience in a broad range of practice areas, especially cases similar to your own.</p><p>Choosing the right personal injury lawyer to help you may be one of the most pivotal decisions you make in your life because it often affects the amount of compensation you receive. When a qualified, well-respected <a href="http://www.harrybateslaw.com/">San Antonio injury lawyer</a> fights for you, there is a greater chance you will receive a full, fair settlement, which will give you and your family peace of mind. </p><p><b>Contact us today</b></p><p>You need to be comfortable with your law firm because the rest of your life may depend on the outcome your case. Our firm represents those seriously injured, and families of those wrongfully killed, in accidents caused by the negligence of others. Please call us at 1-877-716-3777, or fill out our online contact form to set up a free, initial consultation and case evaluation. Get to know us at our offices at 630 Broadway, San Antonio, TX 78215. </p><!--more-->When you are injured due to the willful or negligent actions of another, a personal injury law firm can help you receive compensation commensurate with your injuries and the circumstances of your case. '
