ky</b></p><p>Even if you are a victim of a hit-and-run by an uninsured driver, you can seek recourse by establishing negligence on the part of the property owner or filing a claim against an insurance policy. Call our offices to schedule a consultation to review your case.</p><p>Contact&#160;our <a href="http://www.bfzlaw.com/what-we-do/">Covington&#160;car accident</a> lawyers&#160;at (859) 795-4493 to schedule your free initial consultation. Our Covington lawyers are on call 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>'
