aS'\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Holidays are one of the most\r\ndangerous times for drivers for many reasons. Here in San Diego it is a very big problem on the highways. There are more cars and motorcycles on the roads and streets in qustion\r\nbecause people are traveling to get to a family gathering, to the airport to\r\nboard a flight if family is not local or to the stores to purchase holiday\r\ngifts. All in all, holidays tend to be one of the busiest times of the year for roadways. If you are in SD, southern California then you may require a <a href="http://www.sandiegocaraccidentattorney411.com">San Diego motorcycle accident Attorney</a>\r\nor car crash lawyer to assist you there, especially if personal injury or wrongful death is involved in the said vehicle accident. . Another reason why the roads and interstates are getting more and more dangerous is because drivers are driving\r\nafter attending a gathering or party where they have consumed large amounts of\r\nalcohol. They leave, get behind the wheel of their cars to drive home when they\r\nshouldn&#8217;t. Intoxicated holiday drivers pose a huge risk for other drivers and\r\npassengers on the road. If you have been a victim of a drunk driver, contact a\r\ncar or motorcycle accident attorney to receive a case evaluation. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><b>Tips for Avoiding Accidents During the Holidays</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">There are several precautions\r\nthat people can take and keep in mind in order to avoid a costly and\r\npotentially fatal car accident over the holiday season. Some things that\r\ndrivers should do include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpFirst">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nLimit alcohol\r\nconsumption and avoid drunk driving or drowsy driving</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDo not use your cell\r\nphone, car GPS or text while you are driving and avoid any other distractions\r\nthat may exist. Get directions beforehand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nKeep a safe distance\r\nbetween cars</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDo not speed or drive\r\ntoo fast for the conditions</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDrive with your lights\r\non at all times of the day</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDo not allow friends and\r\nfamily members to drive drunk</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpMiddle">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nReport any drivers that\r\nappear to be driving drunk to police</p>\r\n\r\n<p text-indent: -0.25in;" class="ListParagraphCxSpLast">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nWait until the following\r\nmorning to drive home if you are drunk or have a friend or taxi take you home</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Accidents during the holidays\r\ncan be quite tragic when the mood is supposed to be festive. Avoid crashes by\r\nfollowing the tips listed above. If you have suffered personal injury in a auto\r\ncollision then contact a car accident attorney who can inform you of your\r\nrights and options for filing a claim to get compensation. </p><!--more-->Find out how to stay safe on the road, whether on a cycle, bike, auto or other vehicle.'
