h their appellate, commercial, real estate, estate planning, expungement and personal injury&#160;representation needs.</p><!--more--><p>This blog concerns a lawsuit brought by the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission (EEOC) against&#160;the New York law firm of Kelley Drye &amp; Warren for age discrimination.&#160;</p>'
