aS'\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">A Pinellas Park resident suffered very serious injuries when\r\na car pulled directly into out of a parking lot and directly into the path of\r\nthe motorcyclist. Montgomery Smith (19-years of age) was heading southbound on\r\nTyrone Boulevard when the driver of a Ford F-250 was exiting the Home Depot\r\nparking lot and failed to yield the right-of-way to the motorcycle.&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">If you have followed our <a href="http://www.dolmanlaw.com">blog</a>, we have sadly harped on the\r\nongoing theme that drivers often fail to see motorcycles for a myriad of\r\nreasons, which has led to a number of avoidable tragedies.&#160;&#160; Unfortunately, automobile operators\r\noftentimes do not operate their vehicles with due caution for other\r\ndrivers.&#160; Further, many drivers are\r\nsimply guilty of distracted driving due to the proliferation of cell phones and\r\nother hand held devices which often capture the attention of drivers and\r\ndistract them from their main obligation.&#160;\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">As a Clearwater motorcycle accident <a href="http://www.dolmanlaw.com">attorney</a>, I often note\r\nthat many of my clients were injured as a result of a driver who failed to\r\nnotice them.&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;Many drivers simply fail to allow the\r\nmotorcyclist full use of their respective traffic lane and provide the proper\r\nfollowing distance to enable a sudden stop or deceleration.&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">If you have been injured as a result of a Clearwater motorcycle\r\naccident, call us today at: (727) 451-6900 for a free consultation and case\r\nevaluation.&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Dolman Law Group is your Pinellas County motorcycle accident\r\nlaw firm.&#160; Conveniently located in\r\ncentral Pinellas County, Dolman Law Group is a short commute for motorcycle\r\ninjury victims residing in St. Petersburg, Tampa, Pinellas Park, Largo,\r\nSeminole, Clearwater Beach, Madeira Beach, Indian Rocks, Sand Key, Palm Harbor,\r\nDunedin and Safety Harbor.&#160; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Matthew A. Dolman, Esq., is a Pinellas County motorcycle accident\r\nattorney.&#160; A resident of Clearwater, Matt\r\nfocuses much of his practice on representing individuals injured as a result of\r\na motorcycle accident, automobile accident, trucking accident, and drunk\r\ndriving.&#160; </p><!--more-->If you have followed our blog, we have sadly harped on the\r\nongoing theme that drivers often fail to see motorcycles for a myriad of\r\nreasons, which has led to a number of avoidable tragedies.'
