tp://www.nyelderlaw.net/" target="&#95;blank">The Law Firm of Lance P. Armstrong</a> protect your rights and your assets.&#160;Contact&#160;us at (718) 477-7700 or visit us at&#160;<em>900 South Avenue, Suite 401, Staten Island, NY 10314.</em></p><p /><!--more-->The&#160;<a href="http://www.nyelderlaw.net/">Staten Island elder care lawyer</a>&#160;provides the legal guidance, services and advocacy enabling them to achieve their goals of preventing loss of assets due to the cost of long-term care and taxes.'
