her days in the year. The\r\nholiday is a special time of the year when people attend family gatherings\r\nwhere people end up consuming large amounts of food and alcohol. Many drivers\r\nend up getting behind the wheel when it isn&#8217;t the best idea to do so. Sometimes\r\nthey get in the car late at night to make the drive back home since some have\r\nto work the very next day. Here in Orange County we have had a lot of lethal tragedies involving wrongful death attorney court cases, sad to say.<p class="MsoNormal">.</p><!--more-->Exploring the causes of vehicle crashes in the U.S.'
