aS'Volvo and Lotus announce recalls<p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p>from USA Today</p><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p><a href="http://content.usatoday.com/communities/driveon/post/2011/10/volvo-and-lotus-announce-recalls/1">http://content.usatoday.com/communities/driveon/post/2011/10/volvo-and-lotus-announce-recalls/1</a></p><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><div>Simon W. Johnson</div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div><a href="mailto:swj@swjlawoffice.com">swj@swjlawoffice.com</a></div><div><a title="Law Officebr /br /\r\nofbrbrbrbr /br /br /\r\n/br /br /br /\r\n/br /br /br /br /br /\r\n/brbr /br /br /br /br /br /br /\r\n/br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /\r\nSimonbr /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /br /\r\nW. Johnson" href="http://www.swjlawoffice.com/" target="&#95;blank">Law Offices of Simon W. Johnson</a></div><div><a title="Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/#!/InjuryLawyerOH" target="&#95;blank">Twitter</a></div><div><a title="Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/#!/profile.php?id=612530703" target="&#95;blank">Facebook</a></div>'
