aS'<div id="body">\r\n\t\t<p>According to the CDC or the Center for Disease\r\nControl and Prevention report, head injuries are the main reason for\r\nmortality in both kids and grownups. It is estimated that about 44% of\r\ntotal head injuries will end up in death. Generally there are five main\r\ncauses for traumatic brain injuries; they are happening from accidents and because of violence or assault. If you\r\nobtain brain injury in an accident then without any delay contact <a  rel="nofollow" href="http://brain.ehlinelaw.com/types/" title="brain injury lawyers">Ehline Law Firm PC</a> to get some compensation.</p><p>Brain\r\nis the most important part of the body so if it is damaged then your\r\nlife will face a drastic change and it surely affects your normal life.\r\n<b>Let us discuss about the types of head injuries</b> Amnesia is one\r\nof the brain injuries which can be prevented and it is not permanent\r\nbrain damage. In this condition the person will forget what happened\r\nbefore and during the accident. Here are some head injuries which may\r\nshow off soon after the accident and gradually the condition will\r\nworse. Some of the examples of these kinds of injuries include\r\nlacerations, abrasions, tenderness, bruises, and other types of head\r\ninjuries may be very detrimental.</p><p>Check out some of the most\r\ncommon types of head injuries which are cause due to accidents include\r\nLoss of consciousness, Brain contusion, Concussion, Skull fracture and\r\nHematoma. These injuries are very dangerous. <b>How to prevent you from these types of head injuries</b>\r\nFollow all possible precautionary measure that can protect you from\r\naccidents and head injuries. Here are some of the common precautions\r\nbut are very effective.</p><ul><li>The important precautionary measures are wear a helmet while riding a bike and also carry some safety equipments.</li><li>It is better to wear bright color dress while riding; this is because you will be visible even