aS'Former Humble Civic Center Director Johnnie Ray Scroggins has settled a lawsuit against the City of Humble for unlawful termination due to the Texas&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/whistleblower-rights/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">Whistleblower</a>&#160;Act.<p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">Scroggins first filed the&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/whistleblower-rights/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">Whistleblower</a>&#160;suit against the city November 2012 when he was fired after working for the City of Humble for more than seven years.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#8220;We participated in mediation with and have reached a settlement agreement acceptable to both parties,&#8221; Scroggins said about the case.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">According to Harris County Court Documents, &#8220;Scroggins has been diligent and hardworking as the Director of the Humble Civic Center. In October 2010, Scroggins was informed that he would have to cash a check made payable to Scroggins and deliver cash payments to Humble police officers, working security jobs for the Civic Center.&#8221;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">After these request is when Scroggins repeatedly reported his concerns about the cash payments of the Humble police officers on numerous occasions.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#8220;Within ten days of his most strenuous complaint about the unlawful cash payments to the police officers, Scroggins was told that there was an issue regarding the sale of city lawnmowers from March 2012. Scroggins was told that he could either resign or would be terminated,&#8221; the court documents read.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">The court documents continue to state that at no point between the sale of the lawnmowers in March and the ultimatum was Scroggins reprimanded, written-up or questioned about the sale of the lawnmowers.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">According to information in the Observers&#8217; article from September 2012 about Scroggins&#8217; termination, City of Humble City Manager Darrell Boeske said city records appear to indicate that the money procured from the alleged improper sale, $4,500, flowed back into city coffers and no funds seemed to be missing.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#8220;We have a receipt where we received the money, but as a rental of the ballroom. It is the same equal amount, so you have to make the assumption that that&#8217;s what the money was,&#8221; Boeske said. &#8220;There is no money missing from that sale that I know of.&#8221;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">Nevertheless, Boeske wrote in the termination letter to Scroggins that &#8220;it is no longer in the city&#8217;s best interest&#8221; to continue his employment.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">On Aug. 10, 2012, Scroggins sent an email to his superiors complaining about the procedure which the checks were issued to Scroggins in the amount owed to the police officers for their security service at the Humble Civic Center.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">He was officially terminated Aug. 13, 2013 and informed the City of Humble of his&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/whistleblower-rights/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">Whistleblower</a>&#160;claim in writing Aug. 30, 2012 since there is no grievance procedure allowed.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">Now that both parties have settled out of court they will not have to appear at the court date.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">If you have questions about&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/whistleblower-rights/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">whistleblower rights</a>,&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/report-fraud/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">please contact us</a>.</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">To learn more about&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/types-of-fraud/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">fraud</a>,&#160;please visit our website:&#160;<a href="http://standuptofraud.com/site/" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">www.StandUpToFraud.com</a></p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;">Article by Dan Christensen, visit:&#160;<a href="http://www.miamiherald.com/2013/08/30/3596707/for-profit-college-that-ripped.html" color: blue; text-decoration: none;">www.MiamiHerald.com</a>&#160;</p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;"></p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;"></p><p margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(251, 253, 255); line-height: 21px; color: rgb(15, 18, 39); font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;"><sub>The Linesch Firm provides news and opinion articles as a service to our readers. &#160;Often these articles come from sources outside of our organization. &#160;Where possible, the source is documented within each article as well as a link to the article&#8217;s source. &#160;For more information about <a href="http://lineschfirm.com/wp/the-firm/" font-family: verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; text-decoration: none;">The Linesch Firm</a>, please visit our website: <a href="http://www.lineschfirm.com" font-family: verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; text-decoration: none;">www.LineschFirm.com</a>. &#160;If you have questions about employment matters and would like to consult a <a href="http://lineschfirm.com/wp/the-firm/david-j-linesch-esq/" font-family: verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; text-decoration: none;">Board Certified Labor Attorney</a>, please contact our <a href="http://lineschfirm.com/wp/contact/" font-family: verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; text-decoration: none;">Firm</a>.</sub></p>'
