aS'<p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p></p></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><b mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Avoiding Conviction on <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI<p /></a></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">If arrested, know what to do to minimize charges and set the stage for a solid <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI defense</a>. Consider these tips to avoid conviction on a <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI charge</a>:<p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt"><p>&#160;</p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Remember your manners: I said it before and I will say it again. Be respectful, responsive, and otherwise quiet during a police encounter. What you say and how you say it colors the attitude and actions of law enforcement. <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Smile for the camera: On the road and in the station after arrest, maintain courteous and agreeable behavior. Many police units video-record the booking process and chemical testing process. <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Speak up: Call a friend and call your cell phone to create a contemporaneous record of your voice after arrest. Clear, non-slurred communication creates groundwork for establishing sobriety. <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Dear Diary: As soon as possible, write down all events you remember of the time leading to your traffic stop, arrest, booking, and release from jail, including venues visited and witnesses to your behavior and sobriety. Small details count, so write them down. <p /></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; About those tests: Under California law you are required to submit to blood, breath or urine testing after arrest. Possibility of error is present with each test type and the validity of all three tests can be challenged. <p /></p><p class="MsoNormal" MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt">For more information about <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com">San Diego DUI law</a>, please visit our website <a href="http://www.sdcountydui.com/">http://www.SDCountyDUI.com</a> or call us today at 619-777-7777.<p /></p>'
