aS'<p class="WebText">In November 2008, the state of Tennessee published <i>Tennessee Traffic Crash Facts</i>, which contained some alarming 2006 statistics, including the following:</p><ul><li><div class="WebText">179,000 traffic crashes occurred</div></li><li><div class="WebText">Of those crashes, there were 1,284 fatalities</div></li><li><div class="WebText">The crashes also caused 51,603 injuries, with 6,884 of the injuries classified as incapacitating</div></li></ul><p class="WebHeading2">Common Causes of Accidents</p><p class="WebText">Of course, many things can cause a motor vehicle accident, but some of the top causes include these:</p><ul><li><div class="WebBulletList">Bad driving, including driver inattention, speeding, and aggressive driving</div></li><li><div class="WebBulletList">Impaired driving, including use of alcohol or drugs</div></li><li><div class="WebBulletList">Distracted driving caused by talking or texting on cell phones or playing music in the vehicle</div></li></ul><p class="WebHeading2">Why you need a Lebanon criminal defense lawyer</p><p class="WebText">If you were responsible for an auto vehicle accident in Tennessee, you need to consider the cause of your accident.&#160; In a relatively minor accident, such as a fender bender caused by distracted driving, a <a href="http://www.lowerylaw.com/aop/Auto-and-Car-Accident-Law/">Lebanon TN auto accident attorney</a> may provide the legal defense you need.&#160; But, many accidents are caused by criminal offenses, such as Driving Under the Influence (DUI).&#160; </p><p class="WebText">If you were impaired by drugs or alcohol, or committed another criminal offense, you need representation by <a href="http://www.lowerylaw.com/" target="&#95;blank">Lebanon criminal defense&#160;attorney</a> to get the best outcome for your case.</p><p class="WebText">In fact, you cannot anticipate the exact charges that may be brought against you in any accident, minor or serious.&#160; A&#160;Mt. Juliet and&#160;<a href="http://www.lowerylaw.com/aop/Tennessee-criminal-law/">Lebanon criminal lawyer</a> knows the local laws and court system to provide the best possible defense in any motor vehicle accident situation.</p><!--more-->Read about&#160;motor vehicle&#160;accidents in Lebanon and Mt. Juliet, TN'
