aS'Media PA personal injury lawyer, George Rassias of Schmidt, Kirifides &amp; Fridkin settled a home health aid&#8217;s slip and fall case against a homeowner with poor step configuration for $25,000 pre-suit. The matter involved our client who sustained a fractured foot requiring immobilization when she suffered a fall while exiting a client&#8217;s home through a garage door with an insufficient landing. Our client underwent weeks of casting and non-weight bearing followed by approximately twenty (20) physical therapy visits. She also subsequently complained of shoulder discomfort and underwent some physical therapy for that as well. She responded to conservative treatments and returned to work.\r\nThere were causation concerns over the shoulder complaints, and comparative negligence issues were likely to arise. In resolving the case prior to incurring litigation costs, we were able to maximize our client&#8217;s recovery with a fair and reasonable settlement and avoid incurring not only additional costs associated with full blown litigation in a disputed liability slip and fall lawsuit, but also bring the case to closure within a year from the date of injury.\r\n\r\nMedia PA Personal Injury Lawyers of Schmidt, Kirifides &amp; Fridkin Handle Slip &amp; Fall Lawsuits\r\n\r\nThe personal injury lawyers at Schmidt, Kirifides &amp; Fridkin have been representing injured individuals for over 20 years and are dedicated to pursuing fair and reasonable settlements for our client&#8217;s recovery. We work hard to resolve personal injury cases prior to litigation to avoid delays and inconvenience. However, if your case proceeds to trial, our injury attorneys have the knowledge and resources to see injury lawsuits through to the end. We serve clients in throughout Southeastern Pennsylvania, including Philadelphia County, Bucks County, Berks County, Montgomery County, Chester County and Delaware County, as well as throughout the three counties of Delaware. We have offices in Philadelphia and Media, PA, and Wilmington, Delaware. Call us today at 1-877-268-6466 for a free consultation or submit a free online inquiry.<!--more-->Media PA personal injury lawyer, George Rassias of Schmidt, Kirifides &amp; Fridkin settled a home health aid&#8217;s slip and fall case against a homeowner with poor step configuration for $25,000 pre-suit.'
