#2710<br />Philadelphia, PA 19103<br />(215) 665-1600</p><p>For more information regarding our law firm, visit our online profiles: <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps/place?cid=2262441242748800145&q=Galfand+Berger,&hl=en" target="&#95;blank">Google Places</a>, <a href="http://www.merchantcircle.com/business/Galfand.Berger.LLP.Philadelphia.Personal.Injury.Attorneys.215-665-1600">Merchant Circle</a></p><!--more-->Philadelphia law firm, Galfand Berger profiles Attorney Arthur Bugay who has earned&#160;a place in the Million Dollar Advocates Forum and a 2010 spot on the&#160;Pennsylvania Super Lawyer&#8217;s list.'
