aS'<p class="MsoNormal">Our <a href="http://www.buckfirelaw.com/practice&#95;areas/michigan-motorcycle-accident-lawyer-mi-biker-injury-attorney.cfm">Michigan motorcycle accident lawyers</a> at the law offices\r\nof Buckfire &amp; Buckfire P.C have handled many cases that involved the\r\nnegligence of another driver causing a motorcycle accident. Although the public\r\noften thinks that bikers are responsible for motorcycle accidents, statistics\r\nshow otherwise. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Approximately 75 percent of accidents are caused when a motorcycle is hit by a car. Research also shows that motorcyclists are 25 times\r\nmore likely to be involved in a deadly accident than people driving a car, even\r\nthough motorcyclists only make up three percent of registered vehicles. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">An\r\noften-overlooked fact is that the other drivers either fail to respect or pay\r\nattention to motorcycles. In addition, the driver often violates the\r\nmotorcyclists&#8217; right of way and causes the crash in 2/3 of the cases which results in\r\na wide variety of car-motorcycle and truck-motorcycle accidents, including:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Cars rear-ending\r\n     motorcycles</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Cars or trucks failing\r\n     to signal before changing lanes</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Other vehicles making a\r\n     right turn from the center lane and failing to see a motorcycle to their\r\n     right</li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal">Trucks or cars forcing\r\n     motorcycles into a guard rail</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph">?&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;\r\nDrivers running a red light or stop sign without seeing the\r\nmotorcycle</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">For more information\r\nregarding your rights after a Michigan motorcycle accident, call us now at (800) 606-1717 to speak with one of\r\nour Michigan motorcycle accident lawyers about your case. We will start working\r\non your case immediately gathering all the evidence and witness statements to\r\nwin and settle your case.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&#160;</p>'
