aS'<p MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class="MsoNormal">Daniel Duvall and Dan Gilleon <a href="http://www.mglawyers.com/blog/million-dollar-lawsuit-planned-against-reckless-bounty-hunters/">appeared on Prime Time with Taylor Baldwin</a> to discuss their upcoming lawsuit against the Lipstick Bounty Hunters.&#160; The back story:&#160; Daniel Duvall was out on bond.&#160; His bondsman elected to revoke Daniel&#8217;s bond and hired a group of dirt cheap bounty hunters, called the Lipstick Bounty Hunters.&#160;&#160; This group of &#8220;law&#8221; agents are focused on promoting themselves on TV and typically create chaotic situations in attempt to drive ratings for their online web series.&#160; The Lipstick Bounty Hunters attacked Daniel Duvall, as he sat quietly at a restaurant.&#160; They shot rubber bullets at Daniel, used a Taser and sprayed pepper spray.&#160; Daniel suffered numerous injuries and he is currently blinded in his right eye as a direct result of the attack.&#160; Dan Gilleon, a <a href="http://www.mglawyers.com">San Diego personal injury lawyer</a> at Mitchell | Gilleon (<a href="http://www.mglawyers.com/">http://www.mglawyers.com</a>), represents Daniel Duvall.&#160; <p /></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class="MsoNormal">Mr. Gilleon plans to file a lawsuit against the four bounty hunters, the bondsman and the insurer company.&#160; He explains to Taylor, &#8220;You can&#8217;t shoot someone in the eye and expect no one will care about him.&#8221;&#160; Taylor agrees, noting the bounty hunters threw caution to the wind by bringing out a gun in a public place.&#160; Mr. Gilleon is seeking to have the event reviewed as &#8220;an assault and battery, resulting in bodily injury&#8221;.&#160;&#160; Daniel Duvall explains, &#8220;These ladies should be put out of business.&#160; They have weapons and they are shooting at people in public places.&#8221;&#160; <p /></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt" class="MsoNormal">For more information about this lawsuit, or to speak with Dan Gilleon, please visit <a href="http://www.mglawyers.com/">http://www.mglawyers.com</a>. <p /></p>'
