aS'<p>The more points you have on your driver&#8217;s license, the more it will cost you in insurance rates and in possible loss of your license through suspension or revocation. Any moving or safety violation in California can mean more points, more aggravation, and more costs. Maybe you were late for an appointment. Maybe the speed limit&#160;sign wasn&#8217;t clearly visible. Maybe it was an emergency and you broke a traffic rule you wouldn&#8217;t normally break. Or maybe you weren&#8217;t speeding at all.&#160;You may have been stopped for some other reason and the officer decided to give you a moving violation ticket. Whatever the ticket, whatever the reason, you need to make every effort to get those points off your license and off your record.</p><p /><p>California Vehicle Code Violations include:</p><ul><li>Speeding Ticket - 22350 VC</li><li>Driving At Over 100 MPH - 22348 VC (two points, vehicle impound &amp; license suspension)</li><li>Following Too Close or &quot;Tailgating&quot; 21703 VC</li><li>Improper Passing - Unsafe Lane Change - 21658 VC</li><li>Wrong Way on a One-Way Street&#160;&#160;- 21657 VC</li><li>Racing on the Highway&#160; - 23109 (misdemeanor)</li><li>Running a Red Light Ticket - 21453 VC</li><li>Running a Stop Sign Violation - 22450 VC</li><li>Improper Turn - 22107 VC</li><li>Improper U-Turn Ticket - 22102 VC</li><li>Reckless Driving Citation - 23103 VC (misdemeanor)</li><li>Driving without a License - 12500, 12951</li><li>Suspended License 14601 et. seq. VC (misdemeanor)&#160;</li></ul><br /><p>The traffic ticket lawyers at the Takakjian, Sowers &amp; Sitkoff&#160;LLP know every letter of the traffic enforcement law, we know the technical equipment used in traffic enforcement, and we know how to represent your case effectively in a&#160;Southern California traffic court.</p>What can Takakjian, Sowers &amp; Sitkoff LLP do about your traffic violations?<p>Tell us all the details of your traffic stop. How did you happen to get that California speeding ticket or reckless driving ticket? Did the officer have a good reason to pull you over? Did you have any way of knowing the speed limit? Was the stop sign obscured? Did you run a red light to avoid an accident?</p><p>Just because you got a California speeding ticket doesn&#8217;t mean you were in the wrong. This may be a case of an unrealistic speed limit being posted. At Takakjian, Sowers &amp; Sitkoff LLP your traffic ticket lawyer&#160;will check whether there is a valid engineering and traffic survey on file that justifies the posted speed.</p><p /><p>Our attorneys have extensive experience in challenging red light photo tickets. We may&#160;be able to get this ticket dismissed. That will hold down your point total. We may request traffic school &#8211; and that will result in a dismissal when you have successfully completed the school.</p>Don&#8217;t pay the ticket until you talk to our lawyers.Free consultation. 1-866-388-7663<p>Please visit our web site</p><p></p><p><a href="http://www.FormerDistrictAttorneys.com">http://www.FormerDistrictAttorneys.com</a></p><p /><p>If you have a speeding ticket, a suspended license&#160;or any other moving violation ticket&#160;from Los Angeles County, Orange County, Ventura County or elsewhere in Southern California&#160;take action now. Get a Former District Attorney on your side.</p>Takakjian, Sowers &amp; Sitkoff LLP<br />Speeding Traffic Ticket Lawyers<br />Call 24 Hours a Day, 7 Days a Week<br />1-866-388-7663<!--more-->NEARBY OFFICES IN LOS ANGELES, ORANGE AND VENTURA COUNTIES AND THROUGHOUT SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA.HIRE A LOCAL CRIMINAL DEFENSE ATTORNEY!PLEASE CALL FOR A FREE CONSULTATION - REASONABLE FEESPLEASE CALL US IMMEDIATELY!&#160;OUR 24-HOUR PHONE NUMBER IS&#160; 1-866-388-7663'
