e medical bills.  If you were involved in a negligent personal injury, do you just want to leave it to chance-or worse yet, the insurance companies-and &#8220;hope&#8221; that everything just works out&#8230; Or, do you want a personal injury lawyer on your team, one who can protect your rights, give you options and make sure that your future is brighter than it seems immediately following your accident?  If you think you or a loved one may have been involved in a negligent accident and need help determining whether or not you have a case, you need to contact an experienced personal injury attorney as soon as possible to determine what legal options you may have.  For a free and detailed evaluation with a personal injury lawyer at Ledger &amp; Associates, please call 1-800-300-0001 or visit the firm\'s website for more information at <a href="http://www.ledgerlaw.com/">www.ledgerlaw.com</a>.<!--more-->Ledger &amp; Associates has created and is happy to offer you the free iAccident Tool Kit downloadable application for your iPhone, iPod or iPad.'
