aS'<p>\r\n\r\nBrooklyn man killed by drinking Red Bull, $85 million lawsuit alleges</p><p /><p /><p>from nydailynews.com</p><p /><p /><p><a href="http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/brooklyn-man-killed-red-bull-85-million-suit-article-1.1498452">http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/brooklyn-man-killed-red-bull-85-million-suit-article-1.1498452</a></p><p /><p /><p><a href="http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/15/tagblogsfindlawcom2012-decided-idUS241785121820120315">Simon W. Johnson</a></p><div></div><div><a href="mailto:swj@swjlawoffice.com">swj@swjlawoffice.com</a></div><div><a title="Law Office of SWJ" href="http://www.swjlawoffice.com/" target="&#95;blank">Law Office of Simon W. Johnson</a></div><div><a title="Martindale" href="http://www.martindale.com/Law-Offices-of-Simon-W-Johnson/law-firm-31105305.htm" target="&#95;blank">Martindale</a> <a title="Avvo" href="http://www.avvo.com/attorneys/44113-oh-simon-johnson-1939846.html" target="&#95;blank">Avvo</a> <a title="Justia" href="http://lawyers.justia.com/lawyer/simon-wynn-johnson-1490836" target="&#95;blank">Justia</a></div><div><a title="FindLaw" href="http://pview.findlaw.com/lawyer/simon-w-johnson/oh/cleveland/NDY3NzE4NF8x/PP" target="&#95;blank">FindLaw</a> <a title="LawInfo" href="http://www.lawinfo.com/law/clevelandfamilylawattorney/" target="&#95;blank">LawInfo</a> <a title="LawGuru" href="http://www.lawguru.com/answers/atty&#95;profile/view&#95;attorney&#95;profile/sjohnson" target="&#95;blank">LawGuru</a></div><div><a title="LinkedIn" href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=86764647&locale=en&#95;US&trk=tab&#95;pro" target="&#95;blank">LinkedIn</a> <a title="Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/#!/InjuryLawyerOH" target="&#95;blank">Twitter</a> <a title="Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/#!/profile.php?id=612530703" target="&#95;blank">Facebook</a></div><div><a title="Serving Beachwood, Cleveland and Ohio" href="http://businessfinder.cleveland.com/law-offices-of-simon-w-johnson-beachwood-oh.html" target="&#95;blank">Serving Beachwood, Cleveland and Ohio</a></div>'
