n claim filed with FINRA.</p><p>The Securities Law Firm of Tramont Guerra &amp; Nunez, PA, is a nationally recognized, Martindale Hubbell &quot;AV&quot; rated securities law firm.&#160; To request a confidential consultation from a TGN attorney to determine whether you have a viable individual securities arbitration claim for investment losses that exceed $250,000 from a full service brokerage account, contact us on our website.&#160; To speak directly with an attorney, call (888) 834-2171 and ask for Ben Fernandez, Esquire.</p><p></p>'
