aS'<p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">Selective serotonin reuptake inhibitors, or SSRI drugs for short, are used as antidepressants for the treatment of depression, anxiety disorders, and some personality disorders. &#160;It is also not uncommon for some of these drugs to be used to treat diabetic nerve pain and fibromyalgia.</p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">How Do SSRI Drugs Work?</p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">SSRIs block the reabsorption of the neurotransmitter serotonin in the brain. Changing the balance of serotonin seems to help brain cells send and receive chemical messages, which in turn boosts mood.&#160; </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">While patients rely on SSRI drugs to improve their quality of life, these drugs like all drugs come with some type of side effects.</p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">What are Common Side Effects from SSRI Drugs?</p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">It is not uncommon for anti-depressants to increase suicidal tendencies.&#160; If You are taking an anti-depressant and having thoughts of suicide, please call your doctor right away.&#160; Other <a href="http://www.anapolschwartz.com/practices/ssri/paxil-birth-defects.asp">side effects</a> may include, mood and behavior changes, trouble sleeping, panic attacks, aggressiveness or restlessness, among others.</p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">The above side effects are easily noticeable and easy to correct with the proper treatment.&#160; But, there are other side effects that one may not recognize until it is too late. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">Unfortunately, it has recently come to light that women who take anti-depressants while pregnant may pass side effects on to their unborn children, which can result in birth defects such as, atrial and ventrical septal defects of the heart, neural tube defects of the brain and spinal cord, craniosyntosis, and spina bifida, just to name a few. </p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><p>&#160;</p></p><p MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal">For more information on SSRI Drugs and related birth defects, please visit: <a href="http://www.anapolschwartz.com/practices/ssri/ssri-birth-defects.asp">http://www.anapolschwartz.com/practices/ssri/ssri-birth-defects.asp</a></p>'
