aS'<p>What the statistics say about big rig accidents is not at all comforting; in fact these statistics show that twelve percent of all traffic fatality accidents involve a big rig. To add to this four percent of traffic injures involve a big rig. The statistics also show that seventy-seven percent of injured big rig accident injury victims and eighty-six of the fatalities were drivers in a non-commercial vehicle. </p><p>On the other side of these statistics it shows that in even the most serious passenger vehicle and big rig collision the truck driver will in most cases walk away uninjured. The reason for the accident can vary, since each accident is different, but in some cases it is because the truck was unsafe.\r\n \r\nWhat the statistics say about big rig accidents is not good for the person that is in a vehicle, because the injuries for the victims that are not fatally injured are severe. </p><p>The big rig is vehicle that can weigh as much as 40,000 pounds or more if fully loaded and the average car weights about 4,000 pounds. That is a large difference when they collide. The built-in protection measures on the vehicle are no match for this kind of weight smashing into it. This type of big rig accident can happen on any highway and that includes the freeways of San Francisco. The injuries can be extremely severe, like spinal cord injuries that will be a lifetime injury. </p><p>Seatbelts and airbags will not be very helpful when matched against the metal of a big rig. The severe injuries can mean being hospitalized, surgeries, rehabilitation, professional home nursing care and other financial difficulties. This is because with severe injuries there is loss of work and in some cases the injured victim cannot go back to their employment for an extended amount of time or permanently.  \r\n</p><p>While there is little defense against injury when involved in a big rig crash the one avenue the injured victim does have after the accident is to hold the big rig driver and the company that owns the truck in many cases. In order to hold them responsible it will take an experienced San Francisco big rig attorney. </p><p>This is an attorney that specializes in big rig crashes and has the knowledge that is needed to represent a big rig accident injury victim or the family of a victim that was fatally injured. \r\n \r\n\r\nNot just any accident attorney will do after a Long Beach big rig crash.  This is so, because the legal claims can be very complex and the expertise of the attorney that specializes in big rig crashes will understand how the case will need to be handled. </p><p>Ehline Law Firm is your <a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/pages/3272/los-angeles-semi-truck-law.htm">Long Beach Ehline Law Firm PC truck accident attorney</a> who is a truly respected personal injury lawyer Los Angeles County. Our Law offices help people for brain injuries, elder abuse, dog bites, and bicycle accidents at 6700 East Pacific Coast Highway Suite 275, Long Beach, CA 90803 (562) 342-9092. Get a highly aggressive and civil law firm for your burn injury and collison cases.\r\n\r\n</p><!--more-->Ehline Law Firm is your Long Beach truck accident attorney who is a \r\nresepected personal injury lawyer Los Angeles County, and beyond who can\r\n be reached for brain injuries, elder abuse, and even motorcycle \r\naccidents at 6700 East Pacific Coast Highway Suite 275, Long Beach, CA \r\n90803 (562) 342-9092. Get an aggressive law firm for your injury and \r\ncrash cases.'
