r\nCalifornia Car Accidents &#8211; Costs of Serious Injury Crashes\r\n<p>While the costs and economic losses associated with <em>California car accidents</em>\r\n that led to at least one serious injury were not as high as those who \r\nwere killed in crashes, the numbers remain extremely high and difficult \r\nfor any society or economy to absorb.&#160; According to the same body of \r\ndata kept by the state, more than 10,000 people in the state suffered \r\nwhat were described as &#8216;severe&#8217; injuries in California car accidents in \r\n2009.&#160; Each one of these severe injuries led to an average economic loss\r\n of nearly $250,000.&#160; Overall, these crashes led to a total economic \r\nloss of just under $2.7 billion.</p>\r\nHow San Diego Personal Injury Lawyers Can Help\r\n<p>Clearly, when someone is seriously injured or killed in a <em>California car accident</em>,\r\n that person or that family needs help in getting back to as normal a \r\nsituation as possible compared to what existed before the crash.&#160; \r\nFortunately, there are laws in place that allow people forced into this \r\nposition by negligent or reckless driving to take action in an attempt \r\nto recover these losses.</p>\r\n<p>If you or someone you love has been seriously injured or worse in a crash, you need to seek the help of <a title="San Diego personal injury lawyers" href="http://www.mglawyers.com/san-diego-personal-injury.html">San Diego personal injury lawyers</a> who have been fighting for the rights of clients for many years. &#160;Contact <strong>Mitchell | Gilleon</strong> today to schedule a free initial consultation.</p><!--more-->If you or someone you love has been seriously injured or worse in a crash, you need to seek the help of San Diego personal injury lawyers who have been fighting for the rights of clients for many years. &#160;Contact Mitchell | Gilleon today to schedule a free initial consultation.'
