aS'<p>If you have been involved in a car accident and have found yourself in a situation where you have to deal with an over-friendly insurance adjuster, an experienced La Mirada <a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/pages/3140/Auto-Accident-Lawyer-LA.htm">automobile accident</a> attorney will advise you that this may not be the time to begin believing everything that you are told. When dealing with insurance adjusters you need to have your eyes and ears open, ask questions, and take notes.\r\n</p><p>La Mirada Automobile Accidents Pose a Danger to the Area\r\nIn 2006, the SWITRS or Statewide Integrated Traffic Records System of the California Highway Patrol compiled statistics that showed that 182 victims were injured and 5 fatally wounded in car accidents that occurred in La Mirada. There were 29 victims who were injured and one killed in DUI car crashes that occurred. </p><p>There were 8 people injured in bicycle accidents, five deaths resulting from auto accidents, and 13 injured as well as two fatalities due to pedestrian accidents. One car accident resulted in the death of one person in 2008.\r\nThe Process of Dealing with Insurance Adjusters is not Always Easy, and experienced <a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/">car accident attorneys</a> in La Mirada advise clients to keep their guard up when they enter into the process of dealing with insurance adjusters. </p><p>Average accident victims may not be aware of the frustrating process, but adjusters have experience in dealing with these matters on a daily basis, and they are very knowledgeable in their line of business. Some may believe the friendly persona they extend, when what they are really trying to do is get away with paying victims as little as possible in compensation. \r\n</p><p>The Experience of Insurance Adjusters Is Used To Their Advantage\r\nWhen you are negotiating with an insurance adjuster on damages that you have received in a car accident, they are looking for the slightest opening of catching you 