he private owner.&#160; Regardless of where your injury occurs, or who caused it, you need an attorney to help you thread through the complexities of your case.&#160; The Potter Law Offices is experienced in recovering favorable results, at trial or through settlement, in personal injury cases.&#160; The firm can help you seek compensation for medical bills, lost wages, emotional distress, and pain and suffering. </p><p /><!--more--><p><a href="http://www.potterlawoffices.com/attorneys/Cal-Potter/">Clark County Nevada Personal Injury Lawyer</a> Cal Potter has practiced law for more than 3 decades. From the beautiful Lake Meade Recreational Area to the casino\'s in Las Vegas, Cal Potter has worked with thousands of clients who have been injured due to negligence on the part of another person or business. &#160;</p>'
