courtesy of Freking &amp; Betz, LLC, one of the <a href="http://www.frekingandbetz.com/aop/Cincinnati-personal-injury/getting-help/">personal injury law firms in Cincinnati</a>, 513-721-1975.<br />&#160;<br />Freking &amp; Betz, LLC<br />525 Vine Street, Suite 600<br />Cincinnati, Ohio (OH) 45202<br />Phone: 513-721-1975 </p><!--more-->An <a href="http://www.frekingandbetz.com/aop/Cincinnati-personal-injury/">injury attorney in Cincinnati</a> discusses: If you are a victim with a possible personal injury case, finding the right law firm can be the difference between winning a substantial settlement or drowning in legal fees and paperwork.'
