aS'<p>\r\nElder abuse&#8212;the growing problem nationwide and in San Francisco is something everyone should be aware of, since we all age. Many families have older family members that become residents of nursing homes and it is important to know the signs of elder abuse in order to stop it. The nursing home is entrusted to care for the aging adult that can no longer live on their own and might need more care than the family is able to provide. \r\n</p><p>There is physical, mental and financial elder abuse that the nursing home resident can suffer and when it becomes apparent there is a problem the family needs to take action, because these situations can become life threatening to the older adult. This is a person that is in a fragile state of health and any type of abuse should never happen, but when it does the elder abuse attorney might be just the person that is needed to stop the actions taking place. \r\n</p><p>The nursing home patient can be an <a href="http://www.nursingethicsnetwork.org/elder-abuse-are-dirty-words-and-actions-there-is-no-excuse-for-in-redondo-beach.html">elder abuse victim in Redondo Beach</a>, just as easily as being a SD victim, and are unable to defend themselves and often feel too embarrassed when abuse is occurring, which means they might not tell their family members. This leaves it up to the family to play detective every time they visit the nursing home and this means looking for a change in the person&#8217;s demeanor, bruising, check their appearance for cleanliness, because neglect is also <a href="http://www.nursingethicsnetwork.org/">elder abuse</a>. Frequent accidents like falls, broken bones, and other injuries should also be checked out completely. </p><p>The family should show up at different times and on different days to visit the aging adult, this way it can be possible to see what occurs when the nursing home staff is not expecting anyone to visit the victim that is suffering from elder abuse. The family needs to ask questions, every time they visit, which will let the nursing home staff know that they are watching to make sure that their parent, aunt, uncle or other relative is properly being cared for. \r\nElder abuse&#8212;the growing problem nationwide and in San Francisco occurs more often than most people realize and the statistics are frightening. </p><p>The elder abuse attorney will get to the bottom of the problem and they will hold the nursing home and staff accountable when there is elder abuse or neglect occurring. Not only does this stop the elder abuse for the family member, but it can also stop other nursing home residents from suffering elder abuse that do not have visitors. Ehline Law Firm PC is a highly experienced <a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/">San Francisco personal injury attorney</a> and they are awaiting your important telephone call.</p><p>50 Francisco Street #460<br />San Francisco, CA 94133<br />(415) 684-7688</p><!--more-->Not only does this stop the elder abuse for the family member, but it \r\ncan also stop other nursing home residents from suffering elder abuse \r\nthat do not have visitors. Ehline Law Firm PC is a highly experienced San Francisco personal injury attorney and they are awaiting your important telephone call.'
