aS'The Los Angeles located&#160;<a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/city/los-angeles.htm">Michael P. Ehline, Esq.</a>, of Ehline Law Firm PC, says that Motorcycle accident settlements help the biker get back on their feet, when the injuries are caused by negligence of another. This can be the negligent actions of a motor vehicle driver, a defective part or design, and it can be due to roadway maintenance negligence. <p /><p>The most common injuries are caused by the negligent driver. These settlements will typically involve the offending driver&#8217;s insurance company, that is also held accountable. \r\n</p><p><b>The Common Types of Claims\r\n</b></p><p>Motorcycle accident lawsuits will help the rider that was injured hold the negligent party accountable for their actions and recover compensation that will cover medical costs, lost wages and other damages. &#160;Damages&#160;claims can include the injuries that were suffered by the rider, the lost wages, permanent disabilities, and in the case of the family that has lost a wage earner in a fatality claim. The civil complaint for damages is different than auto accident settlements, since every mishap is unique and the injuries suffered are far more severe in two wheeled vehicle crashes.</p><p><b>\r\n\r\nSignificance of a Helmet\r\n</b></p><p>\r\nThe rider has nothing more than their helmet to prevent injuries, they do not have the metal cage, the airbags and seatbelts that protect the driver and passengers in an auto accident. This will also mean the motorcycle settlement amount can be far different from the auto mishap compensation, because the injuries suffered are usually more severe, though not in every claim. </p><p /><p>\r\nThere is a settlement formula that does not really apply to the person that is injured in a motor bike crash. &#160;These settlements when awarded, will relieve some of the financial stress of being injured and unable to work, for permanent disabilities and in many cases for exorbitant and ongoing medical care, and even in home nursing care for the life of the injured rider. </p><b>\r\n\r\nHaving the Right Lawyer is Crucial\r\n\r\n</b><p>One of the most important elements of the motorcycle accident settlements, is having an experienced <a href="http://www.ehlinelaw.com/pages/3237/PracticeAreas&#95;MotorcycleAccident.htm" title="Los Angeles motorcycle accident attorney">Ehline Law of Angeles motorcycle accident attorney</a>. This is crucial when going up against the negligent driver&#8217;s insurance company, who will have experienced counsel representing them, that will fight for the insurance company&#8217;s benefit. It is to their benefit not to pay out claims, and the experienced car accident lawyer in Los Angeles, can prevent you from not winning the amount of compensation you deserve.   Call now at (213) 291-9080.\r\n\r\n</p><!--more-->One of the most important elements of the motorcycle accident lawsuits \r\nor motorcycle accident settlements is having an experienced Los Angeles motorcycle accident attorney.'
